title: Ep - 129 - STEPHANIE HOLLMAN FROM REAL HOUSEWIVES OF DALLAS
description:
Stephanie Hollman from Real Housewives of Dallas discusses life before Bravo’s hit show including her work as a social worker, how she met husband Travis and Brandi, and then opens up about her depression and adjusting to fame. 


Amy Jo Johnson from Season 2 of Below Deck reviews this season thus far and reflects on her time as a stew on the show. 


Podcast and radio host Jazzie Belle reviews this week’s episode of Keeping Up With The Kardashians.
